Smart Holding to Invest in Crimean Resort, Kommersant Says

-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 
2011-03-10T08:17:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/smart-holding-to-invest-in-crimean-resort-kommersant-says.html
JSC Smart Holding , a Ukrainian  investment company , seeks to attract $1 billion to $1.2 billion
in financing for the Balaklava Green resort in Crimea,
 Kommersant-Ukraine  reported, without citing anyone.  The 750 hectare resort will be built in seven to fifteen
years at Balaklava harbor in Sevastopol, the newspaper said.  The project includes 22 hotels as well as cottages, shops
and supermarkets, Kommersant said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net  